title: the battle for middle earth 2 mac
description:
This is the the battle for middle earth 2 for the mac.
Unzip drag to your applications folder and play.
Note: this has been ported with wineskin so no promise that this will work.
Found glitches and bugs: Their is one annoying glitch in the game.
Wen you open up the game its best that you don't skip the intro and the clip or els it can happen that you won't be able to see your mouse.
